news.title: L&T Metro Rail Hyderabad raises Rs 13,119 crore
news.para: ET reported on December 22 that the company was raising up to Rs 13,600 crore including Rs 8,600 crore worth of bonds and CPs of up to Rs 5,000 crore.

news.title: Greater Noida: GNIDA penalises housing society over improper waste management
news.para: ​The action was taken against the Sri Radha Sky Garden society in Sector 16B of Greater Noida West on the instructions of GNIDA CEO Narendra Bhooshan following complaints by its residents, the officials said.

news.title: KGK Realty & Dhoot Infrastructure buys Sare Gurugram under IBC
news.para: The consortium outbid five others bidders, including realty companies Alpha Corp and Signature Global and high net worth individual investors Nikhil Jain, Sunil Kumar Jain and Summer Nanda, they said.
